Thank You for Smoking;;87;;86;;R;;Nick Naylor (Aaron Eckhart), a lobbyist for big tobacco, finds it difficult to balance his duties defending the dangerous substance with those of being a good role model for his young son. Nick's life gets even more complicated when a liberal senator mounts an anti-smoking campaign that he must counter. Based on the novel by Christopher Buckley.;;Comedy,Drama;;Jason Reitman;;2005;;Aaron Eckhart,Maria Bello,Cameron Bright,Adam Brody,Sam Elliott,Katie Holmes,David Koechner,William H. Macy,J.K. Simmons,Robert Duvall,Kim Dickens,Rob Lowe,Todd Louiso,Dennis Miller;;https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/thank_you_for_smoking